                        <interp inst="t18410705-name-439" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES CULMER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 117.) I was there in plain clothes—I saw my brother constable turn round, and he said, "This man has picked my pocket;"—I saw this handkerchief in the prisoner's pos<lb></lb>session, and I took him into custody.</p>
